{"tid":1880832,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有冇人記得今日咩日子...","createTime":"2020-02-15T06:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T12:17:28.000Z","uid":236894,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"186239e42a86f22cbee5d0e38c51c633d4e57b76","tid":1880832,"uid":236894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gyupj3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyupj3U.jpg&h=c2dfae9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇人記得今日咩日子...<br />\n八個月前 616遊行前夕 太古廣場<br />\n<strong>「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭殺港 黑警冷血</span></span>」</strong><br />\n<br />\n八個月前...義士企係太古廣場...<br />\n跌落去...直到不治的時段<br />\n所有人都為佢祈禱<br />\n當得知不治後...<br />\n所有人都痛心<br />\n認為係林鄭逼死義士<br />\n但過咗八個月了<br />\n仲有冇人記得起...<br />\n勿忘義士...勿忘初心...勿忘7千多名手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好因為一個疫情搞到散晒<br />\n我哋仲未光復到香港<br />\n香港一日未獨立 一日未贏<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命 </span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港獨立 唯一出路 </span></strong>"},{"pid":"89d8ed84654ded151cbb45c593f755c6f9aa1c1d","tid":1880832,"uid":236894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:53:35.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"f1e747b46decedcca1870c82c241f28d64602416","tid":1880832,"uid":236894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c9ddc5ffa25de4747cc5f5d4592b9a2ead41ab05","tid":1880832,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路</strong></span></span></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"4bb45cd8e84ce0f648c63